Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵遞員是路癡！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.01,0:23:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潤平是高中生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.21,0:23:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.18,0:23:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非正是對女大學生感興趣的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…性騷擾
